data.description: Price Reduction! This stunning rancher boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1456 sq. ft. of luxurious living space.  Quiet and peaceful this home with it's large lot backs up to protected outlots ensuring privacy.  Just a short walk to the community pool ensures endless summer fun.  One of the few subdivisions that allows you to park your RV or boat in your driveway.  This home is just a short drive over to the boat launch and kayak storage. An outdoor shower allows a refreshing shower after a day at the beach which is only a 10 minute drive. Enjoy the beauty of every season in the comfort of the three season sun room. An outdoor storage shed provides ample storage space for all your outdoor equipment. The outdoor deck is a perfect place for entertaining. The chef in the family will enjoy the fully equipped kitchen with energy efficient stainless steel appliances. The kitchen provides space for a large dining table   A separate laundry room off the kitchen features a slop sink and private entrance.  High quality LVP flooring throughout and tile in the kitchen shows a touch of elegance. The hall bath offers a tub/shower a skylight for superb lighting and a heat lamp for those chilly winter days,  A new roof was installed in 2021. Located off Rt. 54 and close to Harris Teeter and shopping.  Delaware's low taxes sweeten the deal. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home.  Contact me today for a viewing and start living the life you've always dreamed of.
